## Badge

**Path**: `@/components/Badge`  
**Figma**: Roy design system → Badge (node 452:32).

Inline label pill with four variants. Border-radius 4px, height 20px, padding 12px horizontal. Text: medium/paragraph-sm (14px, line-height 1.43).

**Variants** (Figma Types): `default` (slate), `warning` (yellow), `error` (red), `success` (green).

**Props**

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `children` | `React.ReactNode` | Yes | Badge label |
| `variant` | `BadgeVariant` | No | `"default"` \| `"warning"` \| `"error"` \| `"success"` (default: `"default"`) |
| `className` | `string` | No | Applied to the root `<span>` |

**Exports**: `Badge`, `BadgeProps`, `BadgeVariant`.

**Example**

```tsx
import { Badge } from "@/components/Badge";

<Badge variant="default">Label</Badge>
<Badge variant="warning">Warning</Badge>
<Badge variant="error">Error</Badge>
<Badge variant="success">Success</Badge>
```

