## ImageBlock

**Path**: `@/components/ImageBlock`  
**Figma**: Roy design system → Images (node 157:828).

Image block with three sizes: **small** 48×48 (4px radius), **medium** 148×196 (12px radius), **large** 218×218 (12px radius). **Empty**: grey placeholder when no `src`. **Empty-action**: when `onAdd` is set and no `src`, shows add-photo icon (24×24) centered; clickable. **Image-filled**: when `src` is set, shows image; for **large** only, optional `onAction` shows a 40×40 action button (e.g. like) top-right (24px inset), white bg.

**Props**

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `src` | `string \| null` | No | Image URL; omit for empty/empty-action |
| `alt` | `string` | No | Alt text for image |
| `size` | `ImageBlockSize` | No | `"small"` \| `"medium"` \| `"large"` (default `"medium"`) |
| `onAdd` | `() => void` | No | When no src: click shows add icon; triggers on click |
| `onAction` | `() => void` | No | When size is large: action button top-right (e.g. like) |
| `rounded` | `boolean` | No | When false, no border radius (square). Default `true` |
| `className` | `string` | No | Root class |

**Exports**: `ImageBlock`, `ImageBlockProps`, `ImageBlockSize`, `IMAGE_BLOCK_DIMENSIONS`, `IMAGE_BLOCK_RADIUS`.

**Example**

```tsx
import { ImageBlock } from "@/components/ImageBlock";

<ImageBlock size="small" />
<ImageBlock size="small" onAdd={() => openPicker()} />
<ImageBlock size="medium" src={url} alt="Product" />
<ImageBlock size="large" src={url} onAction={() => toggleLike()} />
```

