## ProductListing

**Path**: `@/components/ProductListing`  
**Figma**: Single listing (492:7977); content to right of image (568:2576).

Single listing card: **ImageBlock** large (218×218), no border radius; white content panel (padding 16px, gap 24px). Use **contentPosition**: `"below"` (column, content under image, panel height 209px, seller at bottom) or `"right"` (row, image left, content right, items-stretch so panel height matches image). Content: optional badge; condition row; title; price + optional originalPrice; seller (Avatar 16 + name right).

**Props**

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `imageSrc` | `string` | Yes | Product image URL |
| `imageAlt` | `string` | No | Alt for image |
| `badge` | `string` | No | e.g. "NEW DROP" |
| `conditionLabel` | `string` | No | e.g. "Condition:" |
| `conditionValue` | `string` | No | e.g. "New" |
| `title` | `string` | Yes | Product title |
| `price` | `string` | Yes | e.g. "SEK 1,299" |
| `originalPrice` | `string` | No | Crossed-out price |
| `sellerAvatarSrc` | `string \| null` | No | Seller avatar URL |
| `sellerName` | `string` | Yes | Seller display name |
| `onLike` | `() => void` | No | Like/favorite on image |
| `contentPosition` | `ProductListingContentPosition` | No | `"below"` \| `"right"` (default `"below"`) |
| `className` | `string` | No | Root class |

**Exports**: `ProductListing`, `ProductListingProps`, `ProductListingContentPosition`.

**Example**

```tsx
import { ProductListing } from "@/components/ProductListing";

<ProductListing
  imageSrc={product.imageUrl}
  title="Slayer 10 pack 3 Inch"
  price="SEK 1,299"
  sellerName="LimeStonesoftbaits"
  badge="NEW DROP"
  conditionValue="New"
/>
<ProductListing contentPosition="right" imageSrc={...} title="..." price="..." sellerName="..." />
```

