## Avatar

**Path**: `@/components/Avatar`
**Figma**: avator (44:71); with label below 568:2325, with label right avator-ds-16 (93:2208).

Circular avatar: image when `src` is set, otherwise placeholder (person icon on grey-200). Sizes: 16, 24, 32, 48, 56, 80. With **label**: use `labelPosition`: `"below"` (column, 8px gap, centered, medium/paragraph-sm #121412) or `"right"` (row, 8px gap, items-center).

**Props**

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `src` | `string \| null` | No | Image URL; omit for placeholder |
| `alt` | `string` | No | Alt text for image |
| `size` | `AvatarSize` | No | `16` \| `24` \| `32` \| `48` \| `56` \| `80` (default `32`) |
| `label` | `string` | No | Label next to avatar (position by `labelPosition`) |
| `labelPosition` | `AvatarLabelPosition` | No | `"below"` \| `"right"` (default `"below"`) |
| `className` | `string` | No | Root class |

**Exports**: `Avatar`, `AvatarProps`, `AvatarLabelPosition`, `AvatarSize`.

**Example**

```tsx
import { Avatar } from "@/components/Avatar";

<Avatar size={32} />
<Avatar src={user.avatarUrl} alt={user.name} size={48} />
<Avatar size={80} label="LimeStones.." />
<Avatar size={32} label="TheLifeoftoy" labelPosition="right" />
```

